node.text:
Just Listed in Corona Del Mar - 215 Milford Dr.
Offered at: $5,299,000

Beds: 4
Baths: 6
Square Footage: 6,500
Lot Size: 15,084 sq. ft.

A unique development opportunity in Cameo Shores with ocean and canyon views. The project has been beautifully designed by renowned @tagfront and boasts a contemporary open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 6 bathrooms, a gym with a sauna, a movie theatre, and a large private yard/deck with pool and sunken fire pit. 3-car garage. The square footage is an estimation; the final square footage will be based upon city approval.

node.text:
Just Sold at $15,300,000 - 11 Coral Ridge - Newport Coast

6 Beds / 9 Baths / 9,906 Sq. Ft.

A stunning Santa Barbara style estate in coveted Crystal Cove. This amazing home features 6 bedroom suites, 9 bathrooms, and a guest house with separate entrance. A total of 9,906 sq. ft. of interior space and 773 sq. ft. of beautiful loggias. Large chef's kitchen with custom cabinetry and top-of-the-line appliances. The open floor plan allows for canyon and ocean views. The pool has a Baja lounge with a cabana, complete with a bar/ledge that steps into the pool. Near Crystal Cove beach, hiking trails, Crystal Cove promenade and much more. Co-listed with @luxuryfinehomes
